import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data.sort_values(by='year')
    plt.plot(data['year'], data['net_generation'])
    plt.title('What is the trend of net generation over the years?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Net Generation')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna()
    data = data.sort_values(by='year')
    data = data.set_index('year')
    data = data.groupby(['source']).resample('Y').sum().reset_index()
    data = data.pivot(index='year', columns='source', values='net_generation')
    data.plot(kind='bar', stacked=True)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of net generation by source?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(title='Source', loc='upper left')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['net_generation'] = pd.to_numeric(data['net_generation'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.groupby('source').mean().reset_index()
    plt.bar(data['source'], data['net_generation'])
    plt.title('What is the average net generation by source?', wrap=True)
    plt.ylabel('Average Net Generation')
    plt.xlabel('Source')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data.pivot(index='year', columns='source', values='net_generation')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    heatmap = ax.pcolor(data, cmap='YlGnBu')
    ax.set_xticks(range(len(data.columns)))
    ax.set_xticklabels(data.columns, rotation=45)
    ax.set_yticks(range(len(data.index)))
    ax.set_yticklabels(data.index.strftime('%Y'), rotation=0)
    ax.set_xlabel('Source')
    ax.set_ylabel('Year')
    plt.title('What is the total net generation by year and source?', wrap=True)
    cbar = plt.colorbar(heatmap)
    cbar.set_label('Net Generation')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
